line. Okay, I put "continuous function" here in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:24.080
quotes—he would not have put it in quotes, but I&nbsp;
do because the notion of a continuous function is,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:24.080 --> 00:23:30.160
in fact, highly problematic, as&nbsp;
we'll see later on. But to Jordan,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:30.160 --> 00:23:33.440
he thought he knew what a continuous&nbsp;
function was, and so he thought, well,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:38.400
this is what it is—it's just a pair&nbsp;
of continuous functions specifying the&nbsp;

00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:38.920
